  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Pharmacokinetics of colimycin will be assessed during 12 hours after administration of 2M UI
      colimycin either as an aerosol or after IV injection, the administration being separated by 5
      to 10 days intervals
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
